long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension will keep your YouTube player quality at a desired level.
The extension can be disabled or enabled by pressing on or off.
The quality can be set by pressing the Set Quality button and then selecting the preferred quality.

GitHub Repo: https://github.com/EduardR02/YouTubeQualityExtension
